dmca.title: Photographer Requests Photo Removal [Blogger]
dmca.body:
Hello, 

My name is [Private] and I can be contacted at [Private]@gmail.com

I am writing to request the removal of material on blogspot that is in violation of my copyright under the Digital Millenium Copyright Act. 

The material consists of photographs at the following location: 
http://canadianredwatch.blogspot.com/2007/01/shane-tuttle-aka-jose-martinez-lives.html

I have a good faith belief that use of the copyrighted materials described above on the allegedly infringing web pages is not authorized by the copyright owner, its agent, or the law. 

I swear, under penalty of perjury, that the information in the notification is accurate and that I am the copyright owner or am authorized to act on behalf of the owner of an exclusive right that is allegedly infringed.

Signed, 
[Private]
